.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, pepper
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, paramedic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, house
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Job   | paramedic  | project-manager    |
| Music-Genre           | hip-hop       | house   |
| Sport         | parkour   | biathlon     |

