2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the wooden house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | juice        | soy-milk   |
| Cigar         | aristoff    | vegafina    |
| Job           | firefighter  | bartender  |
| House   | gothic-revival        | wooden     |
